      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to concours standards. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the VANOS system has been fully overhauled, and the rear subframe has undergone proactive reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The limited-slip M Variable Differential Lock operates flawlessly, providing exceptional lateral grip. With zero deferred maintenance and a pristine chassis, this is a rare opportunity for a purist to acquire a mechanically synchronized icon of the analog era.",
